@c COMMON
@end defun

@defun any-bits-set? mask n
[SRFI-60]
@c MOD srfi-60
@c EN
Same as builtin @code{logtest} (@pxref{Basic bitwise operations}).
It is also called @code{any-bit-set?} in srfi-151 (@pxref{R7RS bitwise operations}).
