[SRFI-178]
@c MOD srfi-178
Copies a bitvector @var{bv} in reverse order.  Optional @var{start}
and @var{end} arguments limits the range of the input.

@example
(bitvector-reverse-copy #*10110011100011110000 4 16)
  @result{} #*111100011100
@end example
@end defun

