@defun list->maybe lis
@c MOD srfi-189
[SRFI-189]
If @var{lis} is an empty list, a Nothing is returned.
Otherwise, a Just that has elements in @var{lis} as payload values
is returned.

Note that @code{(list->maybe (maybe->list x))} isn't an identity
